## Examples

```shell
pixi global update
pixi global update pixi-pack
pixi global update bat rattler-build
# Show what would be updated without making changes
pixi global update --dry-run
pixi global update --dry-run pixi-pack
# Output changes in JSON format
pixi global update --json
pixi global update --json pixi-pack
```

